= MM

Supporting MM version: 0.0.x

MM is a Mingle(http://studios.thoughtworks.com/) development console based on Mingle REST API.

MM has the following features integrating with Mingle:

* run transition
* view card list | card
* commit code with running transition

== Download

The latest version of MM can be found at

* http://rubyforge.org/projects/mm/

== Installation

=== Normal Installation

You can install MM with the following command.

  % ruby install.rb

from its distribution directory.

=== GEM Installation

Download and install MM with the following.

   gem install --remote mm

== Online Resources

== MM References

* MM Project Page: http://rubyforge.org/projects/mm
* MM API Documents: http://mm.rubyforge.org

Type "mm help" for an up-to-date help doc.

